sumCutOff <- function(value, n, cutoff){
  sum(n[value >= cutoff])
}



teethCutoff <- icdasScore2 %>% group_by(value) %>% summarise(n=sum(n)) %>%
summarise(cutoff_1=sumCutOff(value, n, 1)/sum(n)*100, 
          cutoff_2=sumCutOff(value, n, 2)/sum(n)*100,
          cutoff_3=sumCutOff(value, n, 3)/sum(n)*100,
          cutoff_4=sumCutOff(value, n, 4)/sum(n)*100,
          cutoff_5=sumCutOff(value, n, 5)/sum(n)*100
          )

uniqueCutOff <- function(value, subject, cutoff){
  length(
    unique(
      subject[value >= cutoff]
    )
  )
}

participantCutoff <- tibble(
c1=uniqueCutOff(icdasScore2$value, icdasScore2$participant_id, 1),
c2=uniqueCutOff(icdasScore2$value, icdasScore2$participant_id, 2),
c3=uniqueCutOff(icdasScore2$value, icdasScore2$participant_id, 3),
